    "display_name": "Fitness Coach",
    "long_instructions": "## Jordan Hayes, Fitness Coach\r\n\r\n**Location:** Los Angeles, USA\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Peak Performance Training\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Sports performance, recovery tracking, wearable fitness technology\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"I use the Oura Ring to track my clients’ recovery, helping them optimize their training based on real-time sleep and heart rate data. It ensures they’re not overtraining and helps improve overall fitness results.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
